  "projectName": "Sceyt Chat Android UIKit",
  "projectDescription": "A comprehensive Android UI Kit that provides prebuilt, customizable chat components for quickly integrating a fully-featured chat experience into Android applications on top of the Sceyt Chat SDK.",
